<h1>Outreach</h1>
<h2 class="custom_h2_white">Breathtaking scenery but with a heartbreaking need for the Gospel.</h2>
<p style="width:750px;font-size:16px">“It took a severe drought in 1993 to break me down and let me surrender my life to God. Being a rancher and a hunter all my life, God’s love was so encompassing that He knew a drought would be the tool to break into my heart. It took me a number of years to understand that my love for the great outdoors and hunting was God given and not my idea! God, in his awesome creativity, put together in HuntSA my two passions - my love for Him and my love for the great outdoors.”<br/><br/>  –Rufus Luttig – owner Hunt SA.  </p>
